vg|30px|link=|alt=Ca]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign U.svg|30px|link=|alt=-U]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Cu-4.svg|30px|link=|alt=Cu]]&nbsp;\n| ca + -u = cu (Mandailing)\n|}\n|}\n\n===Tompi===\n\nIn Mandailing, the diacritic ''tompi'' can be used to change the sound of some characters:\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" summary=\"tompi\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | ha\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n! scope=\"col\" | tompi\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n! scope=\"col\" | ka\n! scope=\"col\" | sa\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n! scope=\"col\" | tompi\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n! scope=\"col\" | ca\n|-\n| [[File:Batak Ha-1, Ka-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ha]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign tompi.svg|33px|link=|alt=tompi]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Ka-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=A]]&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Sa-1, Ca-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ha]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign tompi.svg|33px|link=|alt=tompi]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Ca-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=A]]&nbsp;\n|-\n| [[File:Batak Ha-2, Ka-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ha]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign tompi.svg|33px|link=|alt=tompi]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Ka-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=A]]&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Sa-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ha]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign tompi.svg|33px|link=|alt=tompi]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Ca-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=A]]&nbsp;\n|-\n| [[File:Batak Ha-3.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ha]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign tompi.svg|33px|link=|alt=tompi]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Ka-3.svg|30px|link=|alt=A]]&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Sa-3.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ha]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+\n| [[File:Batak sign tompi.svg|33px|link=|alt=tompi]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =&nbsp;\n| [[File:Batak Ca-4.svg|30px|link=|alt=A]]&nbsp;\n|}\n\n===Placement of diacritics for Ng and H===\nThe diacritics for Ng ([[File:Batak sign Ng.svg|30px|link=|alt=-Ng]]) and H ([[File:Batak sign H.svg|30px|link=|alt=-H]]) are usually written above spacing vowel diacritics instead of above the base character.<br>\nExamples: [[File:Batak syllable ping.svg|baseline|30px|link=|alt=Ping]] ping, [[File:Batak syllable pong.svg|baseline|30px|link=|alt=Pong]] pong, [[File:Batak syllable peh.svg|baseline|30px|link=|alt=Peh]] peh, and [[File:Batak syllable pih.svg|baseline|30px|link=|alt=Pih]] pih.\n\n===Diacritic reordering for closed syllables===\n\nVowel diacritics are reordered for closed syllables (that is, syllables where the final consonant has no vowel).\nConsonants with no vowel are marked by the Batak ''pangolat'' or ''panongonan'' diacritic, depending on the language.\nWhen they are used for a closed syllable (like \"tip\"), both the vowel diacritic and the pangolat/panongonan are written at the end of the syllable.\n\nExamples of closed syllables using ''pangolat'':\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" summary=\"reordering\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | ta\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+&nbsp;\n! scope=\"col\" | vowel\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+&nbsp;\n! scope=\"col\" | pa\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;+&nbsp;\n! scope=\"col\" | pangolat\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | &nbsp;=&nbsp;\n! scope=\"col\" | syllable\n|- align=\"center\"\n| [[File:Batak Ta-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ta]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | \n| \n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak Pa-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Pa]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign mute-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=pangolat]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| [[File:Batak syllable tap.svg|70px|link=|alt=Tap]]\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"border-top:#aaaaaa hidden;\"\n| ta\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | \n| \n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pa\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pangolat\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| tap\n|- align=\"center\"\n| [[File:Batak Ta-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ta]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign E-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=-E]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak Pa-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Pa]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign mute-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=pangolat]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| [[File:Batak syllable tep-2.svg|70px|link=|alt=Tep]]\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"border-top:#aaaaaa hidden;\"\n| ta\n| s