idden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| [[File:Batak syllable tip.svg|84px|link=|alt=Tip]]\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"border-top:#aaaaaa hidden;\"\n| ta\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| i\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pa\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pangolat\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| tip\n|- align=\"center\"\n| [[File:Batak Ta-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ta]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign O-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=-O]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak Pa-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Pa]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign mute-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=pangolat]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| [[File:Batak syllable top.svg|86px|link=|alt=Top]]\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"border-top:#aaaaaa hidden;\"\n| ta\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| o\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pa\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pangolat\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| top\n|- align=\"center\"\n| [[File:Batak Ta-2.svg|30px|link=|alt=Ta]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign U.svg|30px|link=|alt=-U]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak Pa-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Pa]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| [[File:Batak sign mute-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=pangolat]]\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| [[File:Batak syllable tup.svg|70px|link=|alt=Tup]]\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"border-top:#aaaaaa hidden;\"\n| ta\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| u\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pa\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | +\n| pangolat\n| style=\"border-left:#aaaaaa hidden;border-right:#aaaaaa hidden;\" | =\n| tup\n|}\n\n==Punctuation and ornaments==\n\nBatak is normally written without spaces or punctuation (as [[scriptio continua]]). However, special marks or [[Bindu (symbol)|bindu]] are occasionally used.\nThey vary greatly in size and design from manuscript to manuscript.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" summary=\"bindu\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Examples\n! scope=\"col\" | Name\n! scope=\"col\" | Function\n|-\n| [[File:Batak bindu na metek-1.svg|center|30px|link=|alt=bindu na metek]]<hr>[[File:Batak bindu na metek-2.svg|center|30px|link=|alt=bindu na metek]]\n| Bindu na metek (small bindu)\n| Begins paragraphs and stanzas\n|-\n| [[File:Batak bindu pinarboras.svg|center|30px|link=|alt=bindu pinarboras]]\n| Bindu panarboras (rice-shaped bindu)\n| Variant of bindu na metek, serves same function\n|-\n| [[File:Batak bindu judul.svg|center|30px|link=|alt=bindu judul]]\n| Bindu judul (title bindu)\n| Separates a title from the body of the text\n|-\n| [[File:Batak bindu pangolat.svg|center|30px|link=|alt=bindu pangolat]]\n| Bindu pangolat\n| Trailing punctuation\n|}\n\n==Unicode==\n\nBatak script was added to the [[Unicode]] Standard in October 2010 with the release of version 6.0.\n\n===Block===\n\n{{Main|Batak (Unicode block)}}\n\nThe Unicode block for Batak is U+1BC0&ndash;U+1BFF:\n\n{{Unicode chart Batak}}\n\n===Rendering===\n\nUnicode fonts for Batak must handle several requirements to properly render text:\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" summary=\"rendering\"\n|- \n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Rendering Requirements\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\" | Examples\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Latin [[Transliteration|Trans.]]\n! scope=\"col\" | Image\n! scope=\"col\" | Unicode Text\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"vertical-align:top\" | Correct placement of one or more diacritics&nbsp;\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | ke\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak Ke-1.png|33px|link=|alt=Ke]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bc2\u1be9|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | ke (Mand.)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak Ke (Mandailing).png|36px|link=|alt=Ke]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bc4\u1be6\u1be9|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | ping\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak syllable ping.svg|baseline|30px|link=|alt=Ping]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bc7\u1bea\u1bf0|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | reng\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak syllable reng.svg|baseline|30px|link=|alt=Ping]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bd2\u1be9\u1bf0|size=24px}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"vertical-align:top\" | Ligatures with U\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | hu (Mand.)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak Hu-3.svg|30px|link=|alt=Hu]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bc4\u1bee|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | hu (Sima.)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak Ku (Simalungun).png|35px|link=|alt=Hu]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bc3\u1bee|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | gu\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak Gu-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Gu]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bce\u1bee|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | lu\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak Lu-1.svg|30px|link=|alt=Lu]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bde\u1bee|size=24px}}\n|-\n| style=\"vertical-align:top\" | Diacritic reordering for closed syllables\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | tip\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[File:Batak syllable tip.svg|80px|link=|alt=Tip]]\n| style=\"font-size:x-large;text-align:center;font-family:prada,'Noto Sans Batak';\" | {{btk|\u1bd6\u1bea\u1bc7\u1bf2|size=24px}}\n|}\n\n==Gallery==\n\n<gallery widths=\"180\" heights=\"180\" perrow=\"3\">\nFile:Paper Museum in Atlanta 010.JPG|Batak book about the art of divination from a [[rooster]] ([[Robert C. Williams Paper Museum]] in Atlanta, Georgia, USA)\nFile:COLLECTIE TROPENMUSEUM Bamboe tabaks- en wichelkoker met Bataks schrift TMnr 512-4.jpg|Batak script carved into a bamboo tube with wooden stopper ([[Tropenmuseum|Museum of the Tropics]] in Amsterdam, The Netherlands)\nFile:Bamboo with Batak script.jpg|Bamboo inscribed with Simalungun Batak script ([[National Museum of Ethnology (Netherlands)|National Museum of Ethnology in Leiden, The Netherlands]])\nFile:COLLECTIE TROPENMUSEUM Wichelboekje van palmblad TMnr 5991-6.jpg|Batak palm leaf book ([[Tropenmuseum|Museum of the Tropics]] in Amsterdam, The Netherlands)\nFile:COLLECTIE TROPENMUSEUM Wichelboek met formules recepten en voorschriften die worden toegepast door de priester-genezer TMnr 1581-1.jpg|Book of formulas, recipes, and rules applied by Batak priests ([[Tropenmuseum|Museum of the Tropics]] in Amsterdam, The Netherlands)\nFile:Book of Wizards Batak Indonesia.jpg|Magic book used by priests of the Toba Batak tribe ([[National Museum of Ethnology (Netherlands)|National Museum of Ethnology in Leiden, The Netherlands]])\nFile:Manuscript in Toba-Batak language, central Sumatra, early 1800s - Robert C. Williams Paper Museum - DSC00360.JPG|Manuscript in Batak Toba language, central Sumatra, 