atak Script website] with free Batak fonts.\n*http://unicode-table.com/en/sections/batak/\n*[https://digital.soas.ac.uk/LOAA005798/00004 Full Batak manuscript] at SOAS University of London.\n{{Kawi family}}\n{{list of writing systems}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2011}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Batak Script}}\n[[Category:Indonesian scripts]]\n[[Category:Brahmic scripts]]\n[[Category:North Sumatra]]\n[[Category:Batak]]\n[[Category:Scripts encoded in Unicode]]\n", "name_user": "Yeonjikang", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Added an external link)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batak_script"}
